cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.MM 

This paper is primarily focused on computer vision tasks, specifically semantic image segmentation, which falls under the category of cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also heavily utilizes deep learning techniques, which suggests that it may also fall under cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the use of Conditional Random Fields (CRFs) may suggest a connection to cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) and cs.MM (Multimedia).
